044/**
045 * Mock Object for {@code ServletContext} (Version 2.3)
046 */
047public class MockServletContext implements ServletContext {
048    private Log log = LogFactory.getLog(MockServletContext.class);
049    private Map<String, Object> attributes = new HashMap<>();
050    private Map<String, String> parameters = new HashMap<>();
051
052    // --------------------------------------------------------- Public Methods
053
054    public void addInitParameter(String name, String value) {
055        parameters.put(name, value);
056    }
057

062        return attributes.get(name);
063    }

068    }

083    }
